Functional Testing Test cases

| Test Case ID | Test Scenario                          | Test Steps                                 | Expected Result                   | Actual Result | Status    |
| ------------ | -------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ | --------------------------------- | ------------- | --------- |
| TC\_FUNC\_01 | Navigation to payment page after order | Add product → Checkout → Place Order       | Redirected to secure payment page | To be tested  | Pass/Fail |
| TC\_FUNC\_02 | Payment via Card                       | Select Card → Enter details → Enter OTP    | Payment success, status = Paid    | To be tested  | Pass/Fail |
| TC\_FUNC\_03 | Payment via UPI                        | Select UPI → Enter UPI ID → Approve        | Payment successful                | To be tested  | Pass/Fail |
| TC\_FUNC\_04 | Refund process                         | Place order → Request refund               | Refund initiated                  | To be tested  | Pass/Fail |
| TC\_FUNC\_05 | Cancel transaction                     | Start payment → Cancel before confirmation | Order marked as Cancelled         | To be tested  | Pass/Fail |


